<script>
import '@formkit/themes/genesis';

export default {
    name: 'FormComponent',
}
</script>

<template>
    <FormKit type="form">
        <FormKit type="text" label="First Name" placeholder="Jack" name="fname" help="Enter your first name" />
        <FormKit type="text" label="Last Name" placeholder="Shukla" name="lname" help="Enter your last name" />
        <FormKit type="email" label="Email" placeholder="xyz@gmail.com" name="email" help="Enter your Email id" />
    </FormKit>
</template>
